The paper proposes a method to improve the robustness of DNN models against adversarial attacks through adversarial training. This topic is closely related to machine learning and computer vision, which are covered by the cs.LG and cs.CV categories. The paper also involves the use of an SVM with an attention mechanism, which falls under the cs.AI category. Additionally, the paper addresses the issue of adversarial attacks, which is a security concern in machine learning and falls under the cs.CR category. Finally, the paper involves the use of deep neural networks, which is a topic covered by the cs.NE category.
